Wide Tabletop The wide smooth tabletop of the rattan dresser provides an ideal setting for showcasing your favorite plants, photographs, and decorative items. Its sleek and polished surface not only serves as a practical space for daily grooming but also doubles as a stylish display area. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It’s alright- small
reviews.reviewText: The dresser itself is nice looking but it’s on the smaller/shorter side (not a big fan of) so make sure you look at dimensions carefully. I gave it 3 starts because I don’t think it’s worth the $200 plus but it’ll do for my guest room for now.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good qulaity & excellent customer service!
reviews.reviewText: I would’ve given this dresser 5 stars if one of my drawer parts was not off level just a little bit. However, the quality of the wood is excellent and I love it. Drawers open and close really nicely, and when I did notice the issue, I reached out to the seller, and they promptly helped me find a solution.
